headline: JPMorgan Announces Final Cash Distributions for the JPMorgan ETFs
summary: TORONTO, Dec. 31, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- J. P. Morgan Asset Management (JPMAM)* today announced the final December 2025 cash distributions for the below listed JPMorgan ETFs. The JPMorgan ETFs trade on the Toronto Stock Exchange (TSX). Unitholders of record on December 31, 2025 will receive cash distributions payable on January 9, 2026(1) and January 16, 2026(2).
